The paper focuses on image processing and deep learning, which are both central topics in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed guided filtering layer is a building block for deep learning, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The layer involves spatial transformations, which could be related to computer graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
